{"id":148547,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：欧洲足联调查穆帅过激言论/","date":"2011-04-29T08:30:28Z","modified":"2011-04-29T08:30:28Z","title":"简讯：欧洲足联调查穆帅过激言论","content":"<div>\n<p>欧洲足联对皇家马德里教练穆里尼奥的过激言论展开纪律调查。</p>\n<p>此前，他率领的皇家马德里队在欧洲冠军联赛半决赛中0比2输给了巴塞罗那队。</p>\n<p>在赛后的记者会上，穆里尼奥称欧洲足联卷入了长期以来的阴谋帮助巴塞罗那队。</p>\n<p>星期三这两支队伍在进行了火药味十足的比赛之后，纪律调查也针对这两支球队展开。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/O0nR6dgihKKjkIk3fqR8QpcCj-I/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/O0nR6dgihKKjkIk3fqR8QpcCj-I/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/O0nR6dgihKKjkIk3fqR8QpcCj-I/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/O0nR6dgihKKjkIk3fqR8QpcCj-I/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/5ZSufeg_r54\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}